                self.wrap_wsgi = True
```

I think this should actually check `app.propagate_exceptions` because this is what determines whether an exception should be re-raised (and thus propagate to WSGI middleware). This property defaults to `app.testing or app.debug` but if `PROPAGATE_EXCEPTIONS` is set explicitly, it always uses that value.

